        SET_TO_NOTHING_CHAPTER_1_CHAPTER_2_CHAPTER                                                      = 7176,  -- Set to... Nothing. Chapter 1. Chapter 2. Chapter 3. Chapter 4. Chapter 5. Chapter 6. Chapter 7. Chapter 8. Crag Order. Chapter 3 -> Ulmia. Chapter 3 -> Taru. Chapter 5 -> Louver. Chapter 5 -> Tenzen. Chapter 5 -> Ulmia.
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH1_NOTHING_OPENING_READY_SAW                                                     = 7177,  -- What stage of CH1? Nothing. Opening Ready. Saw Jeuno Opening. Saw Up-Jeuno Zone In. Talked to Monb. Emptiness 1 Start! Emptiness Boss 1 Dead! Emptiness 2 Start! Emptiness Boss 2 Dead! Emptiness 3 Start! Emptiness Boss 3 Dead!
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH2_NOTHING_ENTERED_TAV_EVTERED                                                   = 7178,  -- What stage of CH2? Nothing. Entered Tav. Evtered Stronghold. Talked to elder. Opened Sacrarium door. (228) Met Nag at the ladder. Met Nag in the 9%b(:. Met Prishe. Got back your amulet. Heard Ulmia's song. Headed to Bahamut's island. Found the island. Chewed out Tarus. Smacked up the Zilart.
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH3_NOTHING_ARRIVED_IN_GUSTABERG                                                  = 7179,  -- What stage of CH3? Nothing. Arrived in Gustaberg! Heard about airships. Talked to Cid. Met Aldo. choices... Ends of 2 choices... Nag leaves on airship. Met Ulmia at Tenshodo. Saw sick Prishe. Went to Pso'Xja. Whipped Diabolos. Prishe heads back to Tav.
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH4_NOTHING_PRISHE_IS_BACK                                                        = 7180,  -- What stage of CH4? Nothing. Prishe is back in Tav. Talked to Disp. Heard where Ulmia went. Heard about Blueblade Fell. Bugged by the Tarus. Win on Bahamut's island. Heard about Promathia. Heard about Promathia & Sac. Open Sac. door with key. Open Reliq. door with key. Saw Reliq. event. Phishe gets chewed out. Louverance leaves by boat. Talked with Chas. Talked with Anoki in Port San.
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH5_NOTHING_PRISHE_ARRIVES_IN                                                     = 7181,  -- What stage of CH5? Nothing. Prishe arrives in Bas. You hear that vessel is stolen. Arrive in Pso'Xja. Saw event deep in ruins. Enter fourth Promyvion. Find first person. Find second person. Find third Person. Make way with vessel. Beat 4th Prom. boss. Saw Beau. event. Three choice start... Three choice end...
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH6_NOTHING_TALKED_TO_DUCAL                                                       = 7182,  -- What stage of CH6? Nothing. Talked to Ducal Guards. Met at pub. Saw Ulmia cry. Talked with Wolfie. Talked with Eshan. Met with Prishe. Heard all of Eshan's talk. Met Matilde. Heard Cid's rambling. Dock in Tavnazia. Beat armada boss.
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH7_NOTHING_WARP_TO_TAV                                                           = 7183,  -- What stage of CH7? Nothing. Warp to Tav. Arrive in safehold. Talked to 3rd person in Tav. Talked to Tenzen. Went to Jeuno. Met Wolfie. Went to pub. Went to Moval. Heard Cid prep. talk. Cid told you to look for guys. Final meeting over. Gave Suleen letter. Beat Tenzen. Saw 5th Mothercry event. Saw the 3 flashbacks!
        WHAT_STAGE_OF_CH8_NOTHING_ENTERED_AL_TAIEU                                                      = 7184,  -- What stage of CH8? Nothing. Entered Al'Taieu. Checked the Palace Gate. Met Makki. Met Kukki. Met Cherukiki. Damn Palace door won't open. Damn Palace door opened. Smacked up Eventide door boss. Got your amulet back. Saw the 5 tower event. Beat Audience Chamber door boss. Promathia has left the building. Promathia left for the battlefield. Wiped the floor with Promathia. Saw epilogue, heard the song.
        WHAT_CRAG_ORDER_NOTHING_1_CLEAR_HAVEN_T                                                         = 7185,  -- What crag order? Nothing. 1 clear (haven't gone yet). 1 = Holla. 1 = Dem. 1 = Mea. clear (haven't gone yet). = Holla. = Dem. = Mea.
        CH3_ULMIA_STAGE_NOTHING_WENT_TO_N_SAN                                                           = 7186,  -- CH3 Ulmia stage... Nothing. Went to N. San. Met Arneau. Met Chas. Led to Hinaree. Met Hinaree.
        CH3_TARUTARU_STAGE_NOTHING_WENT_TO_WATERS_MET                                                   = 7187,  -- CH3 Tarutaru stage... Nothing. Went to waters. Met I[hr[h. Met Yoran. Heard talk in restaraunt. Met Honoi. Accepted Yoran's offer. Gave item to Yoran. Heard from the three Taru. Met tosuka. Heard Yoran for last time.
        CH5_LOUVERANCE_STAGE_NOTHING_SAW_PICTURE_HEARD_CHIEFTAINESS                                     = 7188,  -- CH5 Louverance stage... Nothing. Saw picture. Heard chieftainess. Talked to Tarupapa. Went to Mov. Caught by Mobs. Brought back by Jabbos. Hears Jabbos confession. Talked with Cid.
        CH5_LOUVERANCE_STAGE_NOTHING_MET_CARBUNCLE_RELEASE_POWER                                        = 7189,  -- CH5 Louverance stage... Nothing. Met Carbuncle. Release power from Kuluu ruins. Head for Qufim. Heard from Ducal Guard. Heard Wolfie's true feelings. Saw event in Delk. Heard Tenzen's rambling about E. Fenril's power released. Heard Cid's speech.
        CH5_LOUVERANCE_STAGE_NOTHING_MET_HINAREE_HEARD_ULMIA                                            = 7190,  -- CH5 Louverance stage... Nothing. Met Hinaree. Heard Ulmia's song. Heard from Chas. Heard from Kerutoto. Mithra's converge. Whipped boss in Chasm. Whipped boss in mountains. Heard Cid's speech.
