        SET_YOUR_MISSION_PROGRESS_NAH_MS05_SAW_SEND                                                     = 7720,  -- Set your mission progress! Nah. MS05_Saw send-off at Lion Springs. MS05_Stood at Allied strategy meeting. MS05_Present day. Saw comet over San d'Oria. MS05_Present day. Met with Halver. MS05_Present day. Paid respects at gravestone. MS05_Present day. Met with white Larzos. MS05_Saw army amassing on Xarcabard. MS05_Got assigned messenger duty. MS05_Delivered message to Windurstian army. MS05_Windurst: preparations complete. MS05_Delivered message to Bastokan army. MS05_Bastok: preparations complete. MS05_Strike force makes for Castle Zvahl. MS05_Operation Snowstorm is GO! MS05_Bifrons joins in the fun. MS05_Shadow Lord pwns Allies. MS05_Operation foiled. Sigh. MS05_Escaped from Castle Zvahl. MS05_Operation Snowstorm are FAIL! MS05_Ragelise dishonorably discharged. MS05_Follow that couple to the Throne Room! MS05_You, Lilisette separated from Cait. MS05_Pwned Haudrale and Aquila. MS05_Defeat. Lilisette vanishes.
        HELLO_FAITHFUL_FANS_MIGHTY_MAIDEN_UKA_HERE                                                      = 7721,  -- Hello, faithful fans! Mighty Maiden Uka here!
        JUST_BY_LOOKING_AT_YOUR_SMILING_FACES_I                                                         = 7722,  -- Just by looking at your smiling faces, I can tell you're all having a great time at this year's Sunbreeze Festival! So, are you rrready for some music? I know we're ready to sing our hearrrts out!
        UM_OR_AT_LEAST_I_AM_WHERE_IN                                                                    = 7723,  -- ...Um, or at least I am. Where in sweet Selbina could Mumor be!?
        OH_WELL_THE_SHOW_MUST_GO_ON_IT                                                                  = 7724,  -- Oh well, the show must go on. It's a little embarrassing to sing by myself, but any entertainer worth her miraclesalt would jump at this opporrrtunity. This is my chance to go solo!
        EVERYONE_FEAST_YOUR_EARRRS_UPON_MY_ASTOUNDING_ARIA                                              = 7725,  -- Everyone, feast your earrrs upon my astounding aria.
        YOUR_CACOPHONOUS_WARBLING_IS_ENOUGH_TO_MAKE_ME                                                  = 7726,  -- Your cacophonous warbling is enough to make me vacate the contents of my stomach. These people are not stupid, either... They know that without your partner, you aren't even worth the stage on which you stand.
        WHO_GOES_THERE                                                                                  = 7727,  -- Who goes there!?
        WHO_INDEED_UNDERSTANDABLE_SINCE_I_BELIEVE_THIS_IS                                               = 7728,  -- Who, indeed... Understandable, since I believe this is the first time I've deigned to grace you with my presence. I am a diva. Does that appellation ring any bells for you, pray tell?
        A_DIVA_THEY_TRULY_EXIST                                                                         = 7729,  -- A diva!? They truly exist!?
        OH_SO_YOU_HAVE_INDEED_HEARD_OF_MY                                                               = 7730,  -- Oh, so you have indeed heard of my kind? No wonder you were once my master's favorite archfiend.
        THOUGH_IN_ALL_TRUTH_THE_TITLE_ARCHFIEND_REFERS                                                  = 7731,  -- Though, in all truth, the title archfiend refers to nothing more than washed-up hacks who possess neither the drive nor the talent to reach for the stars...of divadom!
        YET_NOW_YOU_VE_THROWN_EVEN_THAT_AWAY                                                            = 7732,  -- Yet now you've thrown even that away, settling for a mundane life of belching out dull drivel at vulgar venues. Someone as wretched as you holds no value whatsoever.
        ID_7733                                                                                         = 7733,  -- ...
        OR_DO_YOU_I_HEARD_YOU_ASSOCIATE_WITH                                                            = 7734,  -- Or do you...? I heard you associate with some upstart floozy who dares defy my master and dissuades archfiends from our cause. Do you know where she is?
        WELL_IT_SEEMS_YOU_RE_ALL_ALONE_NO                                                               = 7735,  -- Well, it seems you're all alone. No matter. She'll simply have to wait until I'm finished with you.
        COOOME_NOW_MY_PREEECIOUS_T                                                                      = 7736,  -- Cooome now, my preeecious!t
        OF_COURSE_SOMEONE_OF_MY_SUBLIME_STATURE_WOULD                                                   = 7737,  -- Of course, someone of my sublime stature would never condescend to personally dispatch with a peon like you. This minion should prove more than a sufficient substitute for accomplishing that task.
        THE_CROWD_HERE_MAY_BE_RAUCOUS_BUT_DROWN                                                         = 7738,  -- The crowd here may be raucous, but drown out its pesky din.t Now give yourself up to your dreams, just cast away your strife.Next, let your heavy eyelids fall and drool drip down your chin.t This soothing, tranquil lullaby leaves all bereft of life.
