        YOU_CERTAINLY_ARE_PERSISTENT_MY_MASTER_MUST_HAVE                                                = 7768,  -- You certainly are persistent. My master must have seen... But enough chatter! This time I shall truly send you off into eternal slumber with a special lullaby.
