        WHY_IT_S_THE_PERFECT_UNION_OF_FORM                                                              = 7837,  -- Why, it's the perfect union of form and function! Who could ask for more, kupo?
        WHAT_S_MORE_ITS_CARRYING_CAPACITY_CAN_BE                                                        = 7838,  -- What's more, its carrying capacity can be customized to meet its owner's needs. Greedaloxes and Grand Greedaloxes haven't seen anything like this!
